      <title>舒尔茨拒绝下周进行信任投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/scholz-rejects-opposition-s-call-for-confidence-vote-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨拒绝了保守派反对党领袖弗里德里希·默茨的要求，即他应在下周初举行信任投票，为最早于 1 月中旬举行的选举铺平道路。朔尔茨试图将选举推迟到 3 月。查德·托马斯在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/scholz-rejects-opposition-s-call-for-confidence-vote-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:51:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥储蓄减少资本支出，TC Energy 股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/tc-energy-trp-shares-rise-as-mexico-savings-reduce-capital-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TC Energy Corp. 的股价上涨至四年多来的最高水平，因为这家加拿大管道公司由于墨西哥管道项目的节省而降低了资本支出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/tc-energy-trp-shares-rise-as-mexico-savings-reduce-capital-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:47:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯雷首席执行官称美国大选结果公布将重振交易业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/carlyle-s-schwartz-says-election-s-end-is-relief-factor-will-spur-dealmaking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯雷集团首席执行官哈维施瓦茨表示，总统选举的明确结果将为企业高管和投资者提供更多安全保障，使他们能够做出重大决策并进行更多交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/carlyle-s-schwartz-says-election-s-end-is-relief-factor-will-spur-dealmaking</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:40:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺沃格拉茨称，随着特朗普获胜，Galaxy 迎来今年最大交易日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/novogratz-says-galaxy-registers-biggest-trading-day-of-the-year-as-trump-wins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Galaxy Digital 的亿万富翁创始人迈克尔·诺沃格拉茨表示，随着唐纳德·特朗普在美国总统竞选中获胜，人们对加密货币的兴趣激增，这家数字资产公司周三创下了今年最大的交易日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/novogratz-says-galaxy-registers-biggest-trading-day-of-the-year-as-trump-wins</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾比·约瑟夫·科恩称美国没有经济衰退的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/no-signs-of-recession-in-us-says-abby-joseph-cohen-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚商学院教授、前高盛高级投资策略师艾比·约瑟夫·科恩表示，美国没有出现衰退迹象，经济状况为下一届政府留下了良好的基础。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/no-signs-of-recession-in-us-says-abby-joseph-cohen-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:32:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
